" disable arrow keys
noremap <UP> <NOP>
noremap <DOWN> <NOP>
noremap <LEFT> <NOP>
noremap <RIGHT> <NOP>
inoremap <UP> <NOP>
inoremap <DOWN> <NOP>
inoremap <LEFT> <NOP>
inoremap <RIGHT> <NOP>

" visual mode paste without overwriting register
xnoremap p "_dP
